<p>Today&rsquo;s Premium episode &mdash; and July&rsquo;s last &mdash; starts off with some great Mac tips that your fellow listeners have sent in. How to restore battery life, how to revert Lion&rsquo;s text replacements, validating your backup routine, AppleCare start dates, and more are covered. Then it&rsquo;s on to John F. Braun and Dave Hamilton answering your questions. Topics covered here include diagnosing over-running fans in your Mac, iPod nano&rsquo;s FM radio, 64-bits and Lion, and more. <a href="http://www.macobserver.com/tmo/store/" data-wpel-link="internal">Subscribe to Mac Geek Gab today</a> &mdash; it&rsquo;s just US$25 for 6 months &mdash; and you&rsquo;ll get this episode immediately!</p>
